<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV58">
<l>maraṅkeṭana ṭantaṭarttu mattayāṉai mattakat</l>
<l>turaṅkeṭappu ṭaittōrkompo cittukanta vuttamā</l>
<l>turaṅkamvāypi ḷantumaṇṇa ḷantapāta vētiyar</l>
<l>varaṅkoḷakku ṭantaiyuṭki ṭantamālu mallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O superior Lord who rejoiced walking so that the trees were destroyed,</l>
<l>Attacking a rutting elephant, striking [its] head so that [its] strength was destroyed,</l>
<l rend="indent">And breaking one of [its] tusks!</l>
<l>O [Lord] whose feet measured the worlds, splitting [open] the horse’s muzzle!</l>
<l>Aren’t you the Māl who reclined in Kuṭantai</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the brahmins obtained boons [from You]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
